dct_title_s: Bolivia 1:50,000: Comunidad Mayaya, hoja 6047 I. Serie H731
dct_description_sm: Bolivia. Instituto Geografico Militar. Japan International Cooperation Agency. Kokusai Kyoryoku Jigyoda. North Decimal Degree -15.333300. South Decimal Degree -15.5000. East Decimal Degree -67.5000. West Decimal Degree -68.7500. Alternate title: Comunidad Mayaya, Bolivia. Relief shown by 20 m. supplemented by 10 m. contour interval and spot heights.
